title: Angel's Advocate
description: The unwritten rules of baseball vs, the unwritten rules of MTV's The Challenge. Dry shampoo looks too much like shaving cream (10:52). The origin of a new donut-related beef (16:40). Travis really loves Southern Charm (23:22). Pats fans watching Tom Brady get to the Super Bowl (31:30). Patrick Mahomes needs a new schtick (44:35). Super Bowl ads replacing clydesdales with needles (1:02:00). Super Bowl Media Week bingo (1:12:40). Coach K vs. a college student (1:36:22). The NWHL bubble (1:44:28). Investigating Tony DeAngelo's alleged burner account (1:57:27). Lastly: self-acceptance (2:09:32).
